txt.en: 'You know as well as any that I'm no warrior, but I must search for my father.'
'Lord Angbor's path must be swift, and I do not expect him to delay for a single man.'
'I plan to travel into Upper Lebennin, but I fear I cannot do this alone.'
'Be careful, these streets are still home to the city's vile underbelly.'
'I only hope that we find Lorvegil, and put an end to this ordeal.'
'Lorvegil, I only want to know why. Was there anything to gain from a betrayal like this?'
'I think not. A swift death would be far more than you deserve, Lorvegil.'
'These fools will not keep me from serving justice in my own city!'
'I cannot rest while my father remains lost, [placeholder].'
